basics.name: Ashanique Gray
basics.summary: Diligently coordinates all warehouse activities to keep products moving quickly and meet continuous shipping demands. Highly organized leader with good program management and team-building abilities focused on maximizing efficiency and performance. Proven track record of enforcing best practices in fast-paced environments.

work.name: Express Employment Professionals

work.summary: Authored business correspondence, provided productivity insight, reported on metrics, and carried out special projects.

work.name: Restaurant
work.summary: Serviced over 200 customers per day, managed table setting, restaurant operations, and collaborated with kitchen staff.

education.summary: Working towards bachelors degree. Completed continuing education.

awards.title: Employee Recognition
